The Eye Film-Museum - Amsterdam, the Netherlands. 

A museum dedicated to film, both the preservation and presentation. It preserves both Dutch and foreign films screened in the Netherlands.

Designed by Roman Delugan en Elke Delugan-Meissl. Opened in 2012.

Via @amazearchitecture
